de: Dringende Wintersturmwarnung ertönt, als der Schneefall 48 Zoll erreicht: „Absolut nuklear“. Mehrere Gebiete der Vereinigten Staaten wurden in diesem Winter von Rekordschneefällen und bitterer Kälte heimgesucht, und Syracuse, NY, gehört zu den am stärksten betroffenen Gebieten....
title: Urgent Winter Storm Warning Emerges as Snowfall Reaches 48 Inches: 'Absolutely Nuclear'
description: Multiple areas of the United States have been absolutely hammered by record snowfall and bitter cold this winter, and Syracuse, NY, is among the hardest hit....
en: Urgent Winter Storm Warning Emerges as Snowfall Reaches 48 Inches: 'Absolutely Nuclear'. Multiple areas of the United States have been absolutely hammered by record snowfall and bitter cold this winter, and Syracuse, NY, is among the hardest hit....
la: Urgente Hiems Admonitio Emergit ut Snowfall Reaches XLVIII Unciarum: 'Absolute nuclei'. Plures regiones Civitatum Americae Unitarum a memoria nix et amara frigora hac hieme, et Syracusae, NY, penitus percussae sunt, inter gravissimos ictus est.
